  [Text] <LOCATION>Bratislava</LOCATION>--On 27 <DATE>April 1994</DATE> the <ORGANIZATION>Ministry of 
Foreign Affairs</ORGANIZATION> of the Slovak Republic handed a note to the 
Hungarian side, through the <ORGANIZATION>Embassy</ORGANIZATION> of the Hungarian Republic in 
